Post._content: Welcome to [Hexo](https://hexo.io/)! This is your very first post. Check [documentation](https://hexo.io/docs/) for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in [troubleshooting](https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html) or you can ask me on [GitHub](https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues). ## ### ``` bash $ hexo new "My New Post" ``` Hexo scaffolds ``` bash $ hexo new <> "" ``` : [Writing](https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html) ### ``` bash $ hexo server $ hexo s ``` : [Server](https://hexo.io/docs/server.html) ### ``` bash $ hexo generate $ hexo g ``` : [Generating](https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html) ### () ``` bash $ hexo deploy $ hexo d ``` : [Deployment](https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html) ### *SSL* hexo-deployer-git ``` bash $ npm i hexo-deployer-git --save ``` _config.yml : ``` bash deploy: type: git repo: https://github.com// # example, https://github.com/VicoBlog/vicoblog.github.io branch: main message: [] ``` hexo clean && hexo deploy username.github.io ### Markdown [hexo-renderer-marked](https://github.com/hexojs/hexo-renderer-marked) 3.1.0 markdown hexo-renderer-marked ``` bash $ npm install hexo-renderer-marked --save ``` ``` bash _config.yml post_asset_folder: true marked: prependRoot: true postAsset: true ``` hexo new ""`![]()` java ``` ![](image.png) // ``` image.jpg /2020/01/02/foo/image.jpg /2020/01/02/foo/ `![image](image.jpg)` `` ### srcloading(data-original)JSsrc ``` $ npm install hexo-lazyload-image --save ``` _config.yml ``` lazyload: enable: true # onlypost: false # loadingImg: # eg ./images/loading.gif isSPA: true # ```
